NH5 — Creator & Profile Summary (PRD Addendum)

Last updated: 2025-10-19

0) Positioning (vs. MAL/AniList)

Strategy: NH5 is a daily companion focused on discovery, identity, and social play (quests, badges, cosmetics). It coexists with MAL/AniList as the archival ledger. We win by: creator-led rails, tag-first discovery, P2P rec quests, and session-based rewards.

⸻

1) Creator System (V1) — Summary

Goal: Make creator Top 5/Top 10 lists a native discovery surface.

V1 Features
	•	Verified Creator profiles (handle, avatar, links).
	•	Creator Lists (ranked items with notes, source link to video/VOD).
	•	Follow creators → their new lists appear on Home/Discover rails.
	•	Featured Lists rail in Discover.
	•	Quest tie-in: “Complete [Creator] Top 5” → XP + soft-currency (Stardust) + 1 gacha roll.
	•	Remix (V1.5): clone a list, publish your version.

Data Sketch (tables)
	•	creators, creator_followers, creator_lists, creator_list_items (and optional user_list_remixes, user_list_remix_items).

Risks → Mitigations
	•	Brand/likeness: prefer permission; fallback to generic avatar + link.
	•	Ingestion quality: manual admin queue first.
	•	Spoilers/toxicity: spoiler-blur, reports, rate limits, shadow-mute.

KPIs
	•	Creator follow rate ≥ 25% (new users).
	•	Top 5 quest completion ≥ 35%.
	•	Ratings/session from creator entry ≥ 3.

